    section.source_section
        h2 Usage
        h3 Include template
        +printJsCode('include /specs/ux3/components/tables/templates/tables/tables-tmpl.jade')
        h3 Data
        markdown
            p The following data structure must exist to be able to use Table template.
        +printJson({
            "config": {
                "checkbox": false
            },
            "data": {
                "headings": [
                    {
                        "content": "Publication title"
                    },
                    {
                        "content": "ISSN/ISBN"
                    }
                ],
                "rows": [
                    {
                        "cols": [
                            {
                                "content": "publictaion title 1"
                            },
                            {
                                "content": "Lorem Ipsum"
                            }
                        ]
                    },
                    {
                        "cols": [
                            {
                                "content": "publictaion title 2"
                            },
                            {
                                "content": "Dolor sit amet"
                            }
                        ]
                    }
                ],
                "actions": [
                    {
                        "content": "DELETE"
                    }
                ]
            }
        })

        markdown
            p You can add custom classes to the container elements by passing an array of additional class names in `"addClassNames": ["...", "..."]` field for these elements. If you need to replace the default class name, use `"useClassNames": ["...", "..."]` instead. See the table below for the list of container elements and their default class names.

            table
                thead
                    tr
                        th Container element
                        th Default class name
                        th Description
                tbody
                    tr
                        td `wrapper`
                        td no default class
                        td Main component container

            p `content` contains the content for table cells; use `headings` to provide content for table headers; use `rows` and `cols` to provide content for data cells; use `action` to add action buttons. The content can be plain text or HTML.
    | #{''}

