        h3 Expandable Table
        markdown
            p A table can be made expandable by adding the `expandable` class.
            p `expandable` class is used for styling and to attach JavaScript event handlers. When JavaScript is not enabled, the tables will be initialized as fully visible.
            p Each `td` in `tbody` must have a `data-thead` attribute (generated by the template from heading); it is then used to create title on smaller screens.
            p Use `unlabeled` class for table cells that should be unlabeled on mobile devices.
